  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The Danish Ventral Hernia Database (DVHD) registers 37 different perioperative parameters.
      The aim of present study is to use large-scale data from DVHD to uncover risk factors for
      readmission, reoperation (any indication), death and reoperation for recurrence after
      parastomal hernia repair.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      All principal parastomal hernias registered in the Danish Ventral Hernia Database are
      included in the study. The included patients will be followed in up to 4 years in order to
      identify correlation between technical aspects of the hernia repair and postoperative
      morbidity.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
